<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٣٦٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6401">‌مُوسَى بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيلَ </a>، نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1620">‌حَمَّادٌ </a>، أَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1041">‌ثَابِتٌ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">‌وَقَتَادَةُ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1647">‌وَحُمَيْدٌ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">‌أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a>ذَكَرَ هَذَا الْحَدِيثَ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ أَنَسٌ:</span> فَلَقَدْ رَأَيْتُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٢٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَحَدَهُمْ يَكْدُمُ الْأَرْضَ بِفِيهِ عَطَشًا حَتَّى مَاتُوا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>